705492f-a.title: Brooklyn: Lorimer Street - Bayard Street
705492f-a.text:
Lorimer Street, east side, north from Bayard Street, to Driggs Ave.
Also seen is Driggs Ave., north side, east from Lorimer Street. At the
right is a part of Mc Carren Park.
September 10, 1935.
P. L. Sperr.
NO REPRODUCTIONS.
(2)
The same, a more extensive view, showing Bayard Street in the foreground.
September 10, 1935.
P. L. Sperr.
NO REPRODUCTIONS.
